{"tid":1176313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖) 生果報向「劉鑾雄」狂抽水","createTime":"2019-05-29T06:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T08:26:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b158b247c6d4b4425e275f970b6c94345ad58243","tid":1176313,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10157698186622448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.170516952447%2F10157698186622448%2F&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=a56a7011\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10157698186622448/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/P3Dotu0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3Dotu0.png&h=0bb1dccb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港蘋果日報<br />\n23分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n當你「選擇」愛一個不講人權的國，人權當然不重要。<br />\n#史上最強愚人節整蠱 #唔使講嘢喇我哋<br />\n<br />\n#引渡惡法<br />\n【劉鑾雄撤回送中條例司法覆核申請 聲明：愛國愛港支持港府】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QuVLfP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QuVLfP&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=72d9487a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QuVLfP</a><br />\n<br />\n4月1日報道：<br />\n【大劉直指修例違人權法 猶如烏雲籠罩迫他流亡海外】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Qynqwf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Qynqwf&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=54001aef\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Qynqwf</a><br />\n<br />\n5月15日報道：<br />\n【法庭6月審送中覆核案 大劉：法例一向保障不送中才結婚生仔】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QwhuEf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QwhuEf&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=59211c47\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QwhuEf</a>"},{"pid":"92c152c04018ae068baf73f35d92ebab693a78e8","tid":1176313,"uid":157994,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"cite